title: TVS Motor sales rise to 2,77,123 units in November
description: Domestic two-wheeler sales registered a growth of 9 per cent increasing to 1,91,730 units last month as against 1,75,940 units previous year. The company said its total exports stood at 84,134 units last month as compared with 96,000 units in the same month last year.
